{"tid":1230600,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【引渡惡法】港鐵車長車廂嗌咪： 代埋我去，香港人要加油！","createTime":"2019-06-16T08:50:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T12:39:40.000Z","uid":257760,"like":66,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4d8e8111a32b3760c5bd8e4c2229d52e62fc715f","tid":1230600,"uid":257760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:50:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190616/59721478?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR347OsXyNSSQlJveCTAsH0gL7HYnWNvWoYU1s-YFqbMmLEfwe6o9pkRDT8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190616%2F59721478%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR347OsXyNSSQlJveCTAsH0gL7HYnWNvWoYU1s-YFqbMmLEfwe6o9pkRDT8&d=p84ZIGfbRlzA5dgw%2Bb26WD%2FbAHlNv8jCBJNC2S%2BJHYY%3D&h=dd215596\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190616%2F59721478%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR347OsXyNSSQlJveCTAsH0gL7HYnWNvWoYU1s-YFqbMmLEfwe6o9pkRDT8&h=9185548d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190616/59721478?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR347OsXyNSSQlJveCTAsH0gL7HYnWNvWoYU1s-YFqbMmLEfwe6o9pkRDT8</a><br />\n<br />\n【14:45】網上流傳一段聲音檔，指有港鐵車長利用車廂廣播稱：「遊行麻煩代埋我去，要堅持到底，香港人要加油！」引來大批乘客歡呼拍掌；另外，有市民表示乘港鐵時，聽到港鐵女車長開咪叮囑：「大家萬事小心，加油！」<br />\n政府強推引渡惡法，激起社會各界強烈反彈，雖然特首決定暫緩修例，但民主派表明不會接受，認為惡法必須撤回。有港鐵職員致電《蘋果》，指出有不少同事都堅決反對修例，並希望為保衞香港出一分力，罷工是其中一種選項，但礙於職責所在及種種原因，大家均感到有心無力。<br />\n該名職員講出心聲，指「我哋作為交通運輸嘅一個極重要角色，即使見到有人冇埋條命，點傷痛，都一定要繼續返工，為嘅唔係單單自己前途，而係有幾個原因令我地不能，同時不應該咁做」。<br />\n「1.鐵路一受阻，道路交通一定冇可能承受到負荷，唔講警車，消防車同救護車假設真係要出動，市民點樣讓路都好，都肯定會極為受阻；<br />\n2.關乎車務運作，就係每條線都會有spare crew，即係假設有同事病假，都會由spare頂上，而且一日唔止得一個spare，只係返工時間唔同；另外，有個制度叫『賣血』，即係假設spare都頂唔晒咁多個duty，就會搵人OT，而且係搵嗰個禮拜有2日例假嘅同事，OT錢係『時薪』乘以『要頂嘅duty鐘數』再乘以『1.5』，換句話講，有人罷工都好，都肯定會有人頂上；<br />\n3.鐵路好影響道路交通，假設鐵路癱瘓，換嚟嘅只會係令到想參與集會遊行嘅人好難去到集會地點，所以其實早幾日嘅不合作運動係好無謂，支持嘅人亦唔多，同時反而會令市民大眾造成反感&hellip;&hellip;最重要係，根本係冇實際意義。」"},{"pid":"8dd4f9e5322aaf8258bff56e81cc2d81359491d0","tid":1230600,"uid":257760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:52:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2874df28d03af07ba3633097ca2077c86b9ecaab","tid":1230600,"uid":194398,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:57:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a910eddbb72bad09861968de8f71e43b93b0051","tid":1230600,"uid":257760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:08:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830ca57193f40afb2bde2892534036fc38ca45f3","tid":1230600,"uid":19093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T09:11:02.000Z","msg":"港鐵車長車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"442d767365cd38550d646b1794a3dde2e63a42c9","tid":1230600,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2874df28d03af07ba3633097ca2077c86b9ecaab","tid":1230600,"uid":194398,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T08:57:28.000Z","